##### KDE minimal for trading station
# suite for VPS
# minimal hardware support: only network and displays
# minimal application: only browser, file managers, terminal and text editor
# keep appearance original settings though using some resource
# Sorted by change frequency between distro, high to low
# -> DE: Desktop Environment, Settings Packages
# -> Theming: Themes, Icons, Fonts
# -> DE Intergrated App: File Manager, Preferred Applications
# -> Common App: Applications, AUR Support
# -> Hardware Support: Audio Xodec, Connect Package, Network
# -> Xorg: Input Drivers, Server and Graphics

#---------=> Desktop Environment
## KDE Group
plasma-desktop
## GUI Config and Utils
kscreen
plasma-nm
## Panel Plugin
## Desktop Utils from freedesktop
## Misc Utils
kdesu

